  "detailed_description": "<strong>\"Drifter King Online\"</strong> is an addictive multiplayer race and drift game with numerous vehicles options.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>REAL-TIME MULTIPLAYER</strong>: Enjoy online and real-time multiplayer races to defeat other players.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>SELECT YOUR FAVORITE CAR</strong>: There are many vehicles that you can unlock and select.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>DIFFERENT TRACKS</strong>: Compete with other players or against AI to unlock the best tracks.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>CONQUEST</strong>: This game has an incredible conquest system. You can earn achievement and keep track your stats.</li></ul><br>And many more features that you need to play to discover them!<br><br>What are you waiting for? Come and participate in the exciting races to face the <i>DRIFT KINGS</i> <strong>NOW</strong>!",
